title: Home
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Italian, Western, Swiss
description: Ovo-lacto-vegetarian restaurant run by Swiss and Indian team. Focus of the menu is authentic European cuisine. Offers several vegan options. Has semi-indoor seating (roof but no walls) and tables under the sky and palm trees, all of which have views of the ocean. Relaxed atmosphere with tasteful aesthetics and music.
